// 회원별 휴회/병가 기간 (회비 의무 제외용, 기간 제한 없음)
model MemberLeave {
  id           Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  clubMemberId Int
  startYear    Int
  startMonth   Int      // 1~12
  endYear      Int?
  endMonth     Int?     // 1~12, null = 미정/장기
  reason       String?
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  clubMember ClubMember @relation(fields: [clubMemberId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([clubMemberId])
  @@index([clubMemberId, startYear, startMonth])
}
